text: Múte Inequnaaluk Bourup Egede (; born 11 March 1987) is a Greenlandic politician. He has been the 7th and current Prime Minister of Greenland since April 2021. Things that happened while primeminister: In 2025, the primeminister of Denmark came to Greenland.https://www.nrk.no/urix/frederiksen-pa-gronland_-_-gronland- tilhorer-gronlenderne-1.17369076.
